block content
    - var footeFellow = 'http://admissions.miami.edu/undergraduate/academics/programs-of-distinction/foote-fellows/index.html'
    div#main.bordered.centered    
        h1.text-center Roy Howie
        ul.details.no-separator
            li
                a.link-no-show(href='mailto:roydhowie@gmail.com') roydhowie@gmail.com
            li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-stack-overflow
                a(href='/stackoverflow') royhowie (6.6k)
            li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-github
                a(href='/github') royhowie            
        
            
        .strike #[h2 Education]
        h3 University of Miami
            span.time May 2018
        p.small.tabbed B.S. in Pure Mathematics and in Computer Science
        ul.inline.tabbed
            li 3.920 GPA
            li #[a(href=footeFellow) Foote Fellow]
            li Dean's List (4 of 4)
            li attending on merit scholarship
            //- li (4.000 in computer science, 3.945 in math)
        ul.inline.tabbed
            li Abstract Algebra
            li Real + Complex Analysis
            li Differential Geometry

            li C Programming & Unix
            li Operating Systems
            li Computer Architecture
            li Data Structures & Algorithms
            
        ul.inline.tabbed
            li Fall 2016: Topology
            li Machine Learning
            li Computer Graphics

        .strike #[h2 Work & Projects]
        h3 Gables Tutoring
            span.time May 2014 to June 2016
            span.link #[a(href='//gablestutoring.com') gablestutoring.com]
        p.small.tabbed.
            Built on node.js, the platform serves 1k+ users. Online course
            registration and an interactive, real-time tutoring session scheduler
            developed with express.js and Jade. Automated payment plans & online
            billing via a cron and the PayPal API. Push notifications to tutors
            re client scheduling changes via iCalendar.
        //- p.small.tabbed.
            "Significantly reduced if not eliminated time spent
            bookkeeping." —— owner
            
        h3 BCPL Operating System
            span.time Spring 2016
            span "A" grade
            span.link
                a(href='//github.com/royhowie/os') #[i.fa.fa-fw.fa-github]royhowie/os
        p.small.tabbed.
            Wrote an operating system in BCPL, a predecessor of C. Implemented a
            fully recursive block-tree file system, low-level interrupts, and
            process timesharing using virtual memory.
            
        h3 Geomancer Digitization
            span.time Nov 2014 to Nov 2015
            span.link
                a(href='//github.com/royhowie/geomancy') #[i.fa.fa-fw.fa-github]royhowie/geomancy
        p.small.tabbed.
            Research project with
            #[a(href='http://www.cs.miami.edu/home/ogihara/') Prof. Ogihara] 
            to digitize the centuries-old "Book of Fate" from the UMiami Otto G.
            Richter Library Department of Special Collections.
            
        h3 Plebvote
            span.time Aug 2014 to Nov 2014
            span.link #[a(href='//plebvote.com') plebvote.com]
        p.small.tabbed.
            Live voting platform marketed to local high schools.
            Node.js, websockets, d3.js.

        - var freelance = 'http://royhowie.com/current'
        - var freelanceShort = 'royhowie.com/current'
        h3 Freelance Software Development
            span.link #[a(href=freelance)= freelanceShort]
        p.small.tabbed.
